OL,5, A school has been fined #30,000 for    
OL,6, taking a group of teenage pupils on a  
OL,7, dangerous mountain hike.               
OL,9,FStaff from Gateshead Cheder, an        
OL,10,FOrthodox Jewish school, led 13 boys up 
OL,11,FHelvellyn in the Lake District in March
OL,12,F2020 amid ice and snow.                
OL,14,FA mountain rescue team eventually found
OL,15,Fthe group in darkness and led them to  
OL,16,Fsafety after one boy slipped on ice and
OL,17,Fanother had become separated.          
OL,19,FThe school said "mistakes were made"   
OL,20,Fand health and safety had improved.    
